difference between hubs and swithces:
dono hardware device hote hai , kisi bhi network mein saare computers inse 
connect hote hai,
1) hub ke case mein agar bhut saare computers ek time par request bheje toh 
waha requests ka colloision ho jata in wires, isse data collision bhi kehte, 
because hub jo hota hai woh physical layer par based hota hai,,mtlb koi 
protocol use nahi krta har wire har disha mein request jati hai.
2)switch ke case mein data collsion nahi hota because,yein data link layer par
based hota hai mtlb ethernet protocol follow krta hai,mtlb mac address leker 
chalega and jsse bhejna hai usse hi bhejega.
